{"tid":290102,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"佢係唔係ptgf?","createTime":"2017-06-19T13:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T18:31:02.000Z","uid":78141,"like":46,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"593bce3b7ec70cbfe0952f918bf8e90c47070b1a","tid":290102,"uid":78141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"同佢一直係戀人未滿嘅關係<br />\n佢住港島，我住九龍，所以係極少機會撞到佢<br />\n但有次比我喺九龍一間商場嘅food court見到佢同個男人食飯，食大家口水尾，個男人係典型毒撚樣，睇落有啲成熟<br />\n我即刻whatsapp問佢仲係唔係單身，佢話係，問佢喺邊，佢話喺屋企<br />\n好耐之前問過佢番咩，佢話part-time sales, 問佢番邊間, 佢話唔想講<br />\n但佢係屬於內向，佢喺學校一個傾得埋嘅friend都冇，得幾個男仔groupmate hi bye下<br />\n可能因為佢唔講野，但對住我就好多野講<br />\n佢WhatsApp icon化哂妝，整到好靚咁自拍，仲成日轉icon<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得佢係唔係ptgf?<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ecd0ea56c89aa65ba5c77fed9669e501957cca","tid":290102,"uid":78141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"佢屋企好似幾嚴，有請工人，應該唔愁錢洗"},{"pid":"4d3a2fbbb2827b092ade682b86a289297a94decb","tid":290102,"uid":51388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:51:05.000Z","msg":"Study partner 又唔俾嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb63fde0ee2c9c529a02d5d61500813157370d4d","tid":290102,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:33:04.000Z","msg":"啊哥？"},{"pid":"6ed9aa9f89ab9741c126086473070eacf53aa10b","tid":290102,"uid":78141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啊哥？</blockquote><br />\n知道佢冇阿哥"},{"pid":"e3f23c3f3d3ce24b074df0828ab0a52bbb0baa5b","tid":290102,"uid":78141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T06:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Study partner 又唔俾嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"h